{"tid":2352285,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"舞被朴軫永批「亂又粗糙」！　Rain反擊：JYP會成功不是因為哥","createTime":"2021-01-04T02:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T05:53:01.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"956ca53d243db6180645357be8341a66ee3b36d4","tid":2352285,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"南韓天王Rain（鄭智薰）近日與前老闆朴軫永合作推出單曲《Switch to me》，掀起不小討論度，兩人為了宣傳作品也登上了綜藝節目《認識的哥哥》，交情超過20年的兩人毫不留情地在節目中吐槽對方，其中在他抱怨希望朴軫永不要再對自己的舞指手畫腳時，甚至直言「JYP娛樂會成功，是因為哥不管事了」，引起現場一陣爆笑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5374/d5374279.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5374%2Fd5374279.jpg&h=c049cf78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Rain上節目狂抱怨朴軫永。（圖／翻攝／아는형님 Knowingbros）<br />\n<br />\nRain在被問到跟朴軫永從「師傅與弟子」變成「歌手與歌手」後，有什麼樣的轉變時，直言：「希望別再指責我的舞了。」還抱怨練舞時是對方最常跳錯，而且經常在排練好舞步後，隔天又當場改動，默默在一旁聽著的朴軫永也不甘示弱，表示「覺得智薰果然還是需要我嘮叨他，缺點都還在」，並透露認為Rain到現在還是有很多還沒改掉的跳舞的壞習慣，讓Rain相當無奈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5374/d5374280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5374%2Fd5374280.jpg&h=00bf1b82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲朴軫永認為Rain的舞有很多問題。（圖／翻攝／아는형님 Knowingbros）<br />\n<br />\n朴軫永被姜鎬童問到「Rain需要改進的地方」時，表示：「舞有點凌亂，編舞也有點粗糙。」還直言兩人最近一起練習，還為了宣傳練習了對方的舞，批評Rain「舞怎麼編成這樣」，特別提到前陣子逆行的熱門歌曲《GANG》，開玩笑說道「一開始看到舞直接昏倒」，並給出了許多修正建議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5374/d5374282.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5374%2Fd5374282.jpg&h=429a1cff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲朴軫永不甘示弱直接點出Rain的問題點。（圖／翻攝／아는형님 Knowingbros）<br />\n<br />\n聽完朴軫永一陣「指責」後，Rain也相當無情地反擊：「其實JYP能這麼成功，不是因為哥，現在的JYP是因為哥沒在管事才成功的。」認為對方的想法還停留在以前的年代，早已不適用，兩人一來一往的DISS讓現場主持人們看得津津有味，徐章勳甚至笑著問「今天該不會是兩人最後一次上節目？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5374/d5374284.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5374%2Fd5374284.jpg&h=84f51578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Rain直言JYP娛樂是因為朴軫永不管事了才成功。（圖／翻攝／아는형님 Knowingbros）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v4YLfoOIlW4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv4YLfoOIlW4&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyaHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=f340f9ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v4YLfoOIlW4</a>"},{"pid":"76be153da5de95e791076bbbae5384a14cd40b99","tid":2352285,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:42:08.000Z","msg":"認真的男人好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ff6f7adf5f262c98b00029616e41cc2cba120e","tid":2352285,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76be153da5de95e791076bbbae5384a14cd40b99","tid":2352285,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:42:08.000Z","msg":"認真的男人好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:44:20.000Z","msg":"殺!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0dad58e37d5e035f04183a37507dea3bd30253","tid":2352285,"uid":15371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:15:24.000Z","msg":"JYP Daddy唔會錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9bcaab91c30fc4273c3894998bab519e7702dc","tid":2352285,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"南韓天王爸爸（JYP）"},{"pid":"a25bf94f61ecdc80df02bd5d151ff4015f206b34","tid":2352285,"uid":16659,"